long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Pro Sender - Bulk WhatsApp Sender: Simplify your WhatsApp Business communication and effortlessly connect with your customers by sending bulk messages and translating chats in real time.

Features
🌟 Bulk Messaging: Send personalized messages, images, videos, and documents to multiple contacts simultaneously.
🌟 Excel Integration: Easily import your contact list from Excel and send messages in bulk with just a few clicks.
🌟 Message Templates: Save and reuse message templates for campaigns, promotions, and frequent communications.
🌟 Campaign Scheduling: Plan and schedule campaigns, monitor their progress, and pause or resume them at any time.
🌟 Real-Time Chat Translation: Translate your chats instantly into various languages to communicate with a global audience.
🌟 Group Contact Extraction: Quickly extract and manage contacts from WhatsApp groups.
🌟 Privacy Options: Protect your privacy by blurring chat information when needed.
🌟 Multi-Language Support: Engage with your audience, regardless of their location or language.
🌟 Experience the safest Pro Sender for sending bulk WhatsApp messages and streamline your WhatsApp marketing today!

If you enjoy using Pro Sender, please leave us a positive review—it helps us grow and improve.
